938
01:00:02,530 --> 01:00:05,390
But before I do, I just want to
make sure that what I discussed

939
01:00:05,390 --> 01:00:08,130
is making sense, roughly.

940
01:00:08,130 --> 01:00:08,630
Yeah.

941
01:00:21,750 --> 01:00:23,550
So the question is,
do we apply this

